                        <interp inst="t18471025-name-847" type="surname" value="GILBERT"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18471025-name-847" type="given" value="JOSEPH"></interp>JOSEPH GILBERT</persName>
                  </hi>(<hi rend="italic">policemen, D</hi> 177.) I saw the prisoner and Atkinson together, in Oxford-street—Atkinson spoke to me, and the prisoner said, "For God's sake let me go," and ran away—Atkinson overtook him, and took him to his master's shop—the prisoner had this lid in his left hand, and he gave it to me—he said he had found it in the rubbish in the cellar where was at work.</p>
               <p>(The prisoner received a good character.)</p>
